Czech Teachers in Regional Education (2010–2024)

This repository contains the code, data, and web assets for the "Teachers in Regional Education" project, a longitudinal analysis of teacher demographics, salaries, and qualifications in the Czech Republic.

The project includes:

Automated data collection assets (JSON sitemaps and scraping configurations)

The interactive web report (HTML, CSS, JavaScript)

The analytics dashboard and visualisation suite (Tableau .twbx)

Associated technical documentation and data diaries


All of these components are covered by the MIT License below.

